0  = L0 (Chaos) = F(t), the force that feeds the system
1  = L6 (Purpose) = θ_cube, the attractor
e  = α/β (growth/decay)
π  = ω₀ (the natural frequency, the rhythm)
i  = L5 (Metaconsciousness) = the observer who perceives the traversal as time
```

